# Build Verification

- Run `npm run build` after making code changes that can affect the application.
- Do not consider implementation complete until the build command succeeds.
- If the build fails, fix the errors and re-run `npm run build` until it passes.
- Include the build result in your final update (pass/fail and key error summary if failed).
